<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">

<%- include ('partials/head', {title, meta, og, twitter, schema, canonical}) %>

	<body>
		<!--Start Header -->
		<%- include ('partials/header') %>
			<!--End Header -->

			<!--Breadcrumb Area-->
			<section class="breadcrumb-area banner-1" data-background="images/banner/9.webp">
				<div class="text-block">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-lg-12 v-center">
								<div class="bread-inner">
									<div class="bread-menu">
										<ul>
											<li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
											<li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
										</ul>
									</div>
									<div class="bread-title">
										<h2>About Dadword IT</h2>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<!--End Breadcrumb Area-->

			<!--Start About-->
			<section class="about-agency pad-tb block-1">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-lg-6 v-center">
							<div class="about-image">
								<img src="images/about/company-about.webp"
									alt="SaaS development company USA - Custom web development agency and UI UX design services"
									class="img-fluid" />
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-lg-6">
							<div class="common-heading text-l ">
								<span>About Us</span>
								<h2>About Dadword IT</h2>
								<p>Dadword IT is a custom SaaS and web development agency helping startups and small to mid-sized businesses build scalable, high-performance digital products.</p>
								<p>We specialize in SaaS platforms and modern web applications using technologies like React, Angular, Laravel, and Node.js. From early-stage MVPs to fully scalable production systems, we focus on clean architecture, performance, and long-term maintainability — so your product grows smoothly as your business scales.</p>
								<p>What truly sets us apart is our partnership-driven approach. We don’t just execute tasks — we collaborate closely with founders and business teams to understand goals, users, and challenges. Through transparent communication, predictable delivery, and a strong engineering mindset, we help businesses turn ideas into reliable, market-ready products.</p>
								<p>Trusted by clients across USA, Canada, and Europe, Dadword IT is committed to quality, accountability, and building solutions that create real business impact.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="row in-stats small about-statistics">
								<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4">
									<div class="statistics">
										<div class="statnumb counter-number">
											<span class="counter">20</span>
											<p>Happy Clients</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4">
									<div class="statistics">
										<div class="statnumb">
											<span class="counter">2</span><span>k</span>
											<p>Hours Worked</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-4">
									<div class="statistics mb0">
										<div class="statnumb counter-number">
											<span class="counter">50</span>
											<p>Projects Done</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<!--End About-->

			<!--Start why-choose-->
			<section class="why-choose pad-tb">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row justify-content-center">
						<div class="col-lg-6">
							<div class="common-heading">
								<span>We Are Awesome</span>
								<h2 class="mb30">Why Choose Us</h2>
								<p>We combine technical excellence with a startup-friendly mindset to deliver solutions that are both scalable and business-focused.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="row upset">
						<div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 mt30">
							<div class="s-block up-hor">
								<div class="s-card-icon"><img src="images/icons/research.svg"
										alt="SaaS product development agency - Research and analysis by full stack development company"
										class="img-fluid" />
								</div>
								<h4>Reasearch and Analysis</h4>
								<p>We take time to deeply understand your business model, users, and technical requirements. This allows us to design data-driven, scalable solutions that align with your long-term product vision — not just short-term fixes.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 mt30">
							<div class="s-block up-hor">
								<div class="s-card-icon"><img src="images/icons/chat.svg"
										alt="Web development company Canada - Best web app development services with transparent communication"
										class="img-fluid" />
								</div>
								<h4>Collaboration & Clear Communication</h4>
								<p>We work as an extension of your team. Through regular updates, clear documentation, and open discussions, we ensure alignment at every stage — from planning to deployment.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 mt30">
							<div class="s-block up-hor">
								<div class="s-card-icon"><img src="images/icons/monitor.svg"
										alt="React development agency - Angular development company for custom SaaS builder solutions"
										class="img-fluid" />
								</div>
								<h4>Creative & Scalable Engineering</h4>
								<p>Our engineers combine creativity with strong technical foundations to build modern, future-ready applications. We focus on performance, security, and scalability so your product is ready for growth from day one.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-lg-6 col-sm-6 mt30">
							<div class="s-block up-hor">
								<div class="s-card-icon"><img src="images/icons/trasparency.svg"
										alt="UI UX design agency USA - SaaS MVP development company and product design agency for startups"
										class="img-fluid" /></div>
								<h4>Transparency & Smooth Process</h4>
								<p>No hidden costs. No unclear timelines. We follow transparent processes, realistic estimates, and simple workflows — making collaboration smooth, predictable, and stress-free.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<!--End why-choose-->

			<!--Start Enquire Form-->
			<section class="enquire-form pad-tb">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row light-bgs">
						<div class="col-lg-6">
							<div class="common-heading text-l">
								<span>Contact Now</span>
								<h2 class="mt0">Have Question? Write a Message</h2>
							</div>
